&lt;P style="BOX-SIZING: border-box; MARGIN: 1em 0px"&gt;The User Interface (UI) becomes unresponsive when a time taking operation is executed during an event.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P style="BOX-SIZING: border-box; MARGIN: 1em 0px"&gt;Consider the following button click event where I have simulated a time taking operation by calling Sleep method. In a real scenario, it could be some processing which produces the result to be shown back on the user interface.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;DIV style="BOX-SIZING: border-box"&gt;
